core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:26:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e705e2082f9bb04fff9d90f61a0e60298a3637b9","tid":2083753,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1970fdf42aa34b3bb09049362c9d7180dda89075","tid":2083753,"uid":127575,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c3a68c0abfa5450b0ee7fbaba8d2bcc6fb450cf","tid":2083753,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"香港人, 齊心對抗暴政!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:56:29.000Z","msg":"可能真係最後一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:30:06.000Z","msg":"今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Thanks, Pompeo</span></span></strong>比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8Ysqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=c6afc7b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"1772a2584d0937013847379f99df4130fc8f9e4d","tid":2083753,"uid":54541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T01:46:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1b3e8ab5e12e8cf70d491aa676bfd14cad04188e","tid":2083753,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef799a09469005c0afe7ef951e77090e0b308c2b","tid":2083753,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T02:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zwF3VF2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzwF3VF2.gif&h=730fc11d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa1e51cf02cd452bb0806c38106e3a21bbf1bce4","tid":2083753,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:02:18.000Z","msg":"罷工只要人多先係最大武器囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c379658c1f27048c7ecaf0e48300cb246c093221","tid":2083753,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4078f10fea52c4ba442ae8e8b45cf32fada3b6d5","tid":2083753,"uid":29555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c1215a1c083c07130ddaca68d187c1ac1262a915","tid":2083753,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30